Package: xptr
Type: Package
Title: Manipulating External Pointers
Version: 1.2.0
Date: 2025-10-03
Authors@R: c(person("Randy", "Lai", role = "aut"),
             person("Dirk", "Eddelbuettel", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "edd@debian.org"))
URL: https://eddelbuettel.github.io/xptr/, https://github.com/eddelbuettel/xptr/
Description: There is limited native support for external pointers in the R interface.
 This package provides some basic tools to verify, create and modify 'externalptr' objects.
